title: War of the Roses: She Got a Facebook Message from Another Woman
description: Ava received a message from another woman on Facebook saying she'd been seeing her husband and gave some specific details about his body that makes Ava feel like she's not lying.  So now she's going to try to trap her husband and see if it's true or if this is some random person trying to stir up drama.
